Renders backlink rows for properties declared via "Show backlinks for" on the category.

Reads the category's Show backlinks for property to get the opt-in list of
properties. Only shows the Backlinks header when at least one property has
actual backlink results (aggregate count check across all properties).

For each property with results, renders a conditional row with an #ask query
that finds all pages linking to the current page via that property.

Label is the property's Inverse property label, falling back to property name.

Parameter 1: category name (without namespace prefix)
